@startuml SD_08_QRCheckin
' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE DIAGRAM - QR Code Check-in
' FR-26~FR-28: Scan QR → Validate → Check-in + List
' ============================================================

title **SD-08: QR Code Check-in\n(Scan → Validate → Check-in)**

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #F3E5F5
    ParticipantBorderColor #7B1FA2
    ArrowColor #7B1FA2
}

actor "Staff" as Staff #LightCoral
participant "Browser\n(Mobile)" as Browser #LightYellow
participant "CheckinServlet\n(Controller)" as Controller #F3E5F5
participant "CheckinService" as Service #E8F5E9
participant "TicketDAO" as TktDAO #FFF3E0
database "SQL Server" as DB #F3E5F5

== Step 1: Open Check-in Page ==

Staff -> Browser: Open Check-in for event
Browser -> Controller: GET /staff/checkin\n?eventId={id}
activate Controller
Controller -> Controller: Verify staff\nassigned to this event
Controller --> Browser: Forward → checkin.jsp\n(Camera scanner + Manual input)
deactivate Controller
Browser --> Staff: Check-in page:\n📷 QR Scanner active\n+ Manual code input box

== Step 2: Scan QR Code ==

Staff -> Browser: Aim camera at ticket QR
Browser -> Browser: **jsQR library:**\nDecode QR from camera\n→ Extract JWT token content
Browser -> Browser: Parse ticketCode\nfrom QR data

Browser -> Controller: POST /api/checkin\n{ticketCode, eventId}
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: checkIn(ticketCode, eventId,\nstaffId)
activate Service

' --- Find Ticket ---
Service -> TktDAO: findByTicketCode(ticketCode)
activate TktDAO
TktDAO -> DB: SELECT t.*, o.status,\no.eventId, tt.name as typeName,\no.buyerName\nFROM Tickets t\nJOIN OrderItems oi ON ...\nJOIN Orders o ON t.orderId=o.orderId\nJOIN TicketTypes tt ON ...\nWHERE t.ticketCode = ?
activate DB
DB --> TktDAO: Ticket + Order info
deactivate DB
TktDAO --> Service: ticket
deactivate TktDAO

== Step 3: Validate ==

Service -> Service: **Validate 4 conditions:**\n1. ✅ Ticket exists?\n2. ✅ Correct event?\n3. ✅ Order confirmed?\n4. ✅ Not checked in yet?

alt #FFE0E0 Ticket Not Found
    Service --> Controller: "Ticket not found"
    Controller --> Browser: JSON {success: false,\nerror: "Invalid ticket code"}
    Browser --> Staff: ❌ INVALID TICKET\n(red screen + error sound)

else #FFE0E0 Wrong Event
    Service --> Controller: "Ticket belongs\nto another event"
    Controller --> Browser: JSON {success: false,\nerror: "Wrong event"}
    Browser --> Staff: ⚠️ WRONG EVENT

else #FFE0E0 Already Checked In
    Service --> Controller: "Already checked in\nat {checkedInAt}"
    Controller --> Browser: JSON {success: false,\nerror: "Already checked in\nat 14:30",\nalreadyCheckedIn: true}
    Browser --> Staff: ⚠️ DUPLICATE CHECK-IN\n(yellow screen +\nprevious check-in time)

else #E8F5E9 Valid Ticket ✅

    == Step 4: Check-in ==

    Service -> TktDAO: markCheckedIn(\nticketId, staffId)
    activate TktDAO
    TktDAO -> DB: UPDATE Tickets SET\nisCheckedIn = 1,\ncheckedInAt = GETDATE(),\ncheckedInBy = ?\nWHERE ticketId = ?
    activate DB
    DB --> TktDAO: Updated
    deactivate DB
    TktDAO --> Service: OK
    deactivate TktDAO

    Service --> Controller: CheckinResult {\n  success, ticketCode,\n  buyerName, ticketType,\n  checkedInAt\n}
    deactivate Service

    Controller --> Browser: JSON {success: true,\nbuyerName: "Nguyen Van A",\nticketType: "VIP",\ntime: "14:35:22"}
    deactivate Controller

    Browser --> Staff: ✅ CHECK-IN SUCCESSFUL\n(green screen + success sound)\nName: Nguyen Van A\nType: VIP\nTime: 14:35:22

end

== Check-in Statistics (Real-time) ==

Browser -> Controller: GET /api/checkin/stats\n?eventId={id}
activate Controller
Controller -> DB: SELECT\nCOUNT(*) as total,\nSUM(CASE WHEN isCheckedIn=1\n  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as checkedIn\nFROM Tickets t\nJOIN Orders o ON ...\nWHERE o.eventId = ?\nAND o.status = 'confirmed'
activate DB
DB --> Controller: total=500, checkedIn=234
deactivate DB
Controller --> Browser: JSON {total: 500,\ncheckedIn: 234,\nremaining: 266,\npercentage: "46.8%"}
deactivate Controller
Browser --> Staff: 📊 Stats:\n✅ 234/500 checked in (46.8%)\n⏳ 266 remaining

@enduml
